		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_WONDER_BAWHAWGYI_PAGODA_TOOLTIP">
			<Text>Has a Great Work slot and generates a free Codex. Additional Happiness for each Great Work in this Settlement.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_QUOTE_WONDER_BAWHAWGYI_PAGODA">
			<Text>What we take for self are only nāma and rūpa which arise and fall away.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="LOC_QUOTE_AUTHOR_WONDER_BAWHAWGYI_PAGODA">
			<Text>Khandha Vibhaṅga</Text>
		</Row>

